{"tid":1690230,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] SSD 外置 HDD 電腦認唔到","createTime":"2019-11-03T08:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T06:28:33.000Z","uid":36189,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f885d1031f7c03e6ed8f6271263734198de567f","tid":1690230,"uid":36189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"幫朋友問：<br />\n<br />\n是咁的， Windows 7 插新既 SSD 外置 HDD<br />\n一開波 Windows 都仲識跳個框出黎話搵到個 HDD<br />\n準備搬 file 之制個 HDD 消失左。<br />\n<br />\n我起初以為壞，拎左去舖頭度想換 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢插落佢電腦度係 work 有彈到介面出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之插自己部電腦都唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試過插電源線同埋插 Router, 隻 HDD 都識著燈架！<br />\n係電腦度唔識... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試左 reset USB root Hub 之類的都係無反應<br />\n<br />\n跪求神手巴絲打救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4399cf3a24dc32082a9f99cb20e33face05fd7c","tid":1690230,"uid":36189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"求神手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0a0c1590cf05cafeb133c7470f06ae914dc7e6","tid":1690230,"uid":36189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"求支援 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f5b54fd3dda682644dbb6d2cb18b0fab22e643","tid":1690230,"uid":36189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87210561d86e414a0ff878666f3a138b84632bc7","tid":1690230,"uid":28668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"換個port插<br />\n直接插老母板背後試下先 其他可能供唔夠電/死port"},{"pid":"fe6d82aef878c0e552eb0917138d0d3178a537f5","tid":1690230,"uid":36189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87210561d86e414a0ff878666f3a138b84632bc7","tid":1690230,"uid":28668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"換個port插<br />\n直接插老母板背後試下先 其他可能供唔夠電/死port"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"試過哂所有 USB 頭位都係唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明插緊 keyboard 用得好地地既都試過唔 work  <br />\n謝謝你回應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e857327a85a01747d2340d8c6d90602c935cd3e","tid":1690230,"uid":10439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2809bbbb957e6f529